Task.Name: Read the note for an explanation of the purpose of the template
Task.Notes: The purpose of this template is to support a customer service organization in setting up for the support of a new product. This is a complex topic that could require several schedules to cover all of the components. For simplicity, some of the areas have been noted with only one task, and will need to be developed in greater detail in separate plans. Technology infrastructure is one example of this. We recommend that a separate schedule be created for the development of the technology to support the introduction of a new product. There are several examples of technology templates available for this purpose.

Task.Name: Design of customer service contact scenarios COMPLETE
Develop Levels of Customer Service (Free and Paid)
Identify types of problems to be solved
Determine required skill sets for various support options
Estimate demand for customer support (all options)
Estimate effort to hire new resources
Review output of product review phase
Review anticipated skill sets of support resources
Determine form factor for training content
Identify internal resources that can review training materials
Identify internal resources that can serve as potential trainers
Determine whether additional trainers will be needed
Determine time required to ready external trainers
Create training plan with outputs of Content Development & Training Delivery Phases
Acquire executive sign-off on training plans
Build technology infrastructure plan (separate project plan required)
Determine business objectives of support services
